    {
      "start": 805.92,
      "duration": 4.84,
      "text": "by a single, unwavering resolve"
    },
    {
      "start": 815.44,
      "duration": 7.399,
      "text": "to take revenge on the shark"
    },
    {
      "start": 818.96,
      "duration": 3.879,
      "text": "that had stolen her life."
    },
    {
      "start": 854.28,
      "duration": 4.28,
      "text": "It's Grandpa's Kung Fu instruction book."
    },
    {
      "start": 860.32,
      "duration": 3.88,
      "text": "Kung Fu is not the art of striking an"
    },
    {
      "start": 863.079,
      "duration": 3.76,
      "text": "enemy."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.2,
      "duration": 6.68,
      "text": "It is the art of reading your opponent's"
    },
    {
      "start": 866.839,
      "duration": 7.521,
      "text": "structure. Do not destroy. Perceive the"
    },
    {
      "start": 870.88,
      "duration": 6.8,
      "text": "structure and unravel it."
    },
    {
      "start": 874.36,
      "duration": 5.44,
      "text": "Do not destroy. Perceive the structure"
    },
    {
      "start": 877.68,
      "duration": 3.96,
      "text": "and unravel it."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.8,
      "duration": 4.52,
      "text": "I've got it."
    },
    {
      "start": 881.64,
      "duration": 4.4,
      "text": "What songs should we play at the next"
    },
    {
      "start": 884.32,
      "duration": 4.8,
      "text": "school festival?"
    },
    {
      "start": 886.04,
      "duration": 4.68,
      "text": "Give me some requests. More importantly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.12,
      "duration": 4.0,
      "text": "I just thought of a way to beat the"
    },
    {
      "start": 890.72,
      "duration": 5.16,
      "text": "shark. Easy there."
    },
    {
      "start": 893.12,
      "duration": 6.36,
      "text": "Tell me, how exactly do you plan to stop"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.88,
      "duration": 5.56,
      "text": "that shark? Nano deconstruction."
    },
    {
      "start": 899.48,
      "duration": 3.72,
      "text": "Instead of relying on raw power to"
    },
    {
      "start": 901.44,
      "duration": 3.48,
